Name: Ayu - The Dream Soul -
About the game: Ayu - The Dream Soul - is a surreal horror adventure experience where you control Ayu, a girl who suddenly finds herself in bizarre logicless worlds. Now she has to find out the reason as to why she's in this place. Features: -A mysterious plot. -Dialogues. -Playable flashbacks/cutscenes. -All kinds of different dream worlds. -Exploration of small and large worlds. -Hidden Easter Eggs and Mysteries. -Treasure Chests. -Vendor NPC. * The Game is currently in Early Access phase, a lot of content is already planned for future updates! *
